[
  {
    "from": 4.7,
    "to": 6.04,
    "sid": 1,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "各位同学大家好啊",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 6.04,
    "to": 8.11,
    "sid": 2,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我今天呢想给大家聊一聊",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 8.11,
    "to": 10.37,
    "sid": 3,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "跟电车难题有关的法律问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 10.37,
    "to": 13.67,
    "sid": 4,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那这段时间很多同学希望我讲一讲电车难题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 13.67,
    "to": 16.67,
    "sid": 5,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "相信大家都知道这个著名的哲学命题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 16.67,
    "to": 20.66,
    "sid": 6,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一个疯子呢在一个铁轨上捆了五个无辜的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 20.66,
    "to": 22.94,
    "sid": 7,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "现在一辆火车疾驰而过",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 22.94,
    "to": 25.58,
    "sid": 8,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那你呢可以改变这个火车的轨道",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 25.58,
    "to": 29.03,
    "sid": 9,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "但是另外一个轨道也捆了一个无辜的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 29.03,
    "to": 30.13,
    "sid": 10,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以如果是你",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 30.13,
    "to": 32.83,
    "sid": 11,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "你会不会帮下这个轨道呢",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 32.83,
    "to": 34.59,
    "sid": 12,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "牺牲那个无辜的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 34.59,
    "to": 38.22,
    "sid": 13,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "来保留另外五个无辜人的生命呢",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 38.22,
    "to": 40.3,
    "sid": 14,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这个就叫电车难题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 40.3,
    "to": 43,
    "sid": 15,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我有一次和我的一个朋友讨论这个案件",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 43,
    "to": 45.519,
    "sid": 16,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我的朋友的回答让我大惊失色",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 45.519,
    "to": 46.419,
    "sid": 17,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我的朋友说",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 46.419,
    "to": 50.079,
    "sid": 18,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这都是一些无聊的哲学家设计的无聊的问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 50.079,
    "to": 51.549,
    "sid": 19,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "如果真的有时间",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 51.549,
    "to": 54.67,
    "sid": 20,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "还不如真正的去关心一下你周围的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 54.67,
    "to": 57.73,
    "sid": 21,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "去真正的爱你周围那些具体的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 57.73,
    "to": 62.32,
    "sid": 22,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "不要陷于这种抽象的啊哲学思考毫无意义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 62.32,
    "to": 64.66,
    "sid": 23,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "唉我觉得他说的也蛮有道理的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 64.66,
    "to": 68.44,
    "sid": 24,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "很多时候我们的哲学哲学思考",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 68.44,
    "to": 71.92,
    "sid": 25,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "反而会使得我们对身边的具体人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 71.92,
    "to": 73.87,
    "sid": 26,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "失去了应有的关系",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 73.87,
    "to": 76.39,
    "sid": 27,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "但是既然有很多同学来经常问我",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 76.39,
    "to": 78.58,
    "sid": 28,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "电车难题应该如何解决",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 78.58,
    "to": 81.41,
    "sid": 29,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那我还是想简单的谈一谈我的看法",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 81.41,
    "to": 86.17,
    "sid": 30,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那在哲学观念中显然有两种针锋相对的观点",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 86.17,
    "to": 88.15,
    "sid": 31,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一种是道德主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 88.15,
    "to": 89.53,
    "sid": 32,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一种是功利主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 89.53,
    "to": 91.48,
    "sid": 33,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那在道德主义看来",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 91.82,
    "to": 93.44,
    "sid": 34,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "人只能是目的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 93.44,
    "to": 95.21,
    "sid": 35,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "人不能是纯粹的手段",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 95.21,
    "to": 96.95,
    "sid": 36,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以在任何情况下",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 96.95,
    "to": 100.76,
    "sid": 37,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我能都不能牺牲一个无辜的人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 100.76,
    "to": 102.65,
    "sid": 38,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "去挽救他人的生命",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 102.65,
    "to": 106.7,
    "sid": 39,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "因为没有人有权力去剥夺他人的生命",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 106.7,
    "to": 110.509,
    "sid": 40,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以听天由命就是一种最好的选择",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 110.509,
    "to": 113.269,
    "sid": 41,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那道德主义最骄傲的表述是什么呢",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 113.269,
    "to": 114.889,
    "sid": 42,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "即便天塌下来",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 114.889,
    "to": 117.18,
    "sid": 43,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "正义也要得到践行",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 117.18,
    "to": 121.44,
    "sid": 44,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这就像当年丘吉尔向希特勒德国宣战的时候",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 121.44,
    "to": 123.64,
    "sid": 45,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "曾经做过一个著名的演讲",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 123.64,
    "to": 127.71,
    "sid": 46,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "他说即便我们跟纳粹战斗到底",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 127.71,
    "to": 130.41,
    "sid": 47,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我们英国可能会亡国灭种",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 130.41,
    "to": 132.12,
    "sid": 48,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那就亡国灭种吗",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 132.12,
    "to": 133.84,
    "sid": 49,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "亡国灭种啊",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 133.84,
    "to": 137.48,
    "sid": 50,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "总比做这种亡国奴要强",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 138.399,
    "to": 141.149,
    "sid": 51,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "无论付出任何代价",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 141.149,
    "to": 143.309,
    "sid": 52,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "道义都要得到伸张",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 143.309,
    "to": 144.48,
    "sid": 53,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这是道德主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 144.48,
    "to": 146.94,
    "sid": 54,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "但是功利主义却不这么看",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 146.94,
    "to": 148.1,
    "sid": 55,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "功利主义说",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 148.1,
    "to": 153.2,
    "sid": 56,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那还是要根据事物的结果来决定一种行为",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 153.2,
    "to": 155.23,
    "sid": 57,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "值得做还是不值得做",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 155.23,
    "to": 157.33,
    "sid": 58,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以一边是五个人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 157.33,
    "to": 158.86,
    "sid": 59,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一边是一个人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 158.86,
    "to": 162.49,
    "sid": 60,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那数学公式就会知道五是大于一的呀",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 162.49,
    "to": 166.73,
    "sid": 61,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以功利主义可能就倾向于还是要进行半导",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 166.73,
    "to": 170,
    "sid": 62,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "但是后来呢也有一些功利主义认为",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 170,
    "to": 171.11,
    "sid": 63,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这里面的问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 171.11,
    "to": 174.31,
    "sid": 64,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "可能不单纯是一个五合一的判断问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 174.31,
    "to": 176.94,
    "sid": 65,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这里面最根本的问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 176.94,
    "to": 180.12,
    "sid": 66,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "可能是一个生命能不能比较的问题",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 180.12,
    "to": 183.54,
    "sid": 67,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那也许生命是不能够进行比较的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 183.54,
    "to": 187.17,
    "sid": 68,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "但是当你一旦认为生命不能进行比较",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 187.17,
    "to": 192.14,
    "sid": 69,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "你可能就跟道德主义开始投怀送抱了",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 193.88,
    "to": 197.339,
    "sid": 70,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那我经常跟同学讲一个类似的故事",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 197.339,
    "to": 200.459,
    "sid": 71,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "如果你认为可以牺牲一个人的生命",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 200.459,
    "to": 202.139,
    "sid": 72,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "来保存五个人的生命",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 202.139,
    "to": 205.92,
    "sid": 73,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那可能会导致很多很荒谬的结论",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 206.6,
    "to": 209.74,
    "sid": 74,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "大家可能听过我上课举过的这个例子",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 213.46,
    "to": 214.54,
    "sid": 75,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一个人心坏了",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 214.54,
    "to": 214.96,
    "sid": 76,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "一个人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 214.96,
    "to": 215.86,
    "sid": 77,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "肺坏了一个人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 215.86,
    "to": 216.76,
    "sid": 78,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "皮坏了一个人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 216.76,
    "to": 218.35,
    "sid": 79,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "肝坏了一个人肾坏",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 218.35,
    "to": 220.18,
    "sid": 80,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "结果你从旁边过",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 220.18,
    "to": 222.5,
    "sid": 81,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "医生说小伙子身体怎么样",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 222.5,
    "to": 223.76,
    "sid": 82,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "要不过来一下",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 223.76,
    "to": 226.1,
    "sid": 83,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "牺牲你一个幸福千万家",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 226.1,
    "to": 231.73,
    "sid": 84,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "后来发现这五个年轻人都是北大的高材生",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 231.73,
    "to": 236.82,
    "sid": 85,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "而这个走过来的年轻人是一个智力残疾者",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 236.859,
    "to": 240.3,
    "sid": 86,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那牺牲一个智力残疾者的器官",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 240.3,
    "to": 244.38,
    "sid": 87,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "来挽救五个大有前途的年轻人",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 244.38,
    "to": 246.16,
    "sid": 88,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "大家觉得这合理吗",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 246.16,
    "to": 248.89,
    "sid": 89,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "如果你觉得这个合理",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 248.89,
    "to": 254.14,
    "sid": 90,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那其实纳粹的种族屠杀似乎也有合理之处",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 254.14,
    "to": 256.87,
    "sid": 91,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "纳粹当时就认为",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 256.87,
    "to": 262.39,
    "sid": 92,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "对于没有生存价值的精神病人和这种弱智",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 262.39,
    "to": 264.91,
    "sid": 93,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "可以进行人道毁灭",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 264.91,
    "to": 268.46,
    "sid": 94,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "因为这符合最大多数的最大利益",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 268.46,
    "to": 270.86,
    "sid": 95,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "所以对于我个人而言",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 270.86,
    "to": 274.37,
    "sid": 96,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那种忽视道德的功利主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 274.37,
    "to": 277.34,
    "sid": 97,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "我是非常非常的厌恶的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 277.52,
    "to": 281.48,
    "sid": 98,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "当然如果你讲究道德的功利主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 281.48,
    "to": 283.6,
    "sid": 99,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "这个我是能够接受的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 283.6,
    "to": 285.61,
    "sid": 100,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "很多地方我都提过",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 285.61,
    "to": 287.98,
    "sid": 101,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "其实道德主义和功利主义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 288.74,
    "to": 290.44,
    "sid": 102,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "仔细思考的话",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 290.44,
    "to": 292.789,
    "sid": 103,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "也许并不一定会有冲突",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 292.789,
    "to": 294.229,
    "sid": 104,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "因为柏拉图就说了",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 294.229,
    "to": 295.399,
    "sid": 105,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "什么叫正义",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 295.399,
    "to": 298.189,
    "sid": 106,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "正义就是他行为本身是正当的",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 298.189,
    "to": 300.72,
    "sid": 107,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "而通常又能带来良好的结果",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 300.72,
    "to": 304.5,
    "sid": 108,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "只不过柏拉图把这个通常能带来良好的结果",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 304.5,
    "to": 306.2,
    "sid": 109,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "拉到了永恒",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 307.6,
    "to": 311.97,
    "sid": 110,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "那么英国有一个经典的案件叫连体婴儿案",
    "music": 0
  },
  {
    "from": 311.97,
    "to": 316.14,
    "sid": 111,
    "location": 2,
    "content": "很多同学经常用这个案件来反驳我的观点",
    "music": 0
